Package: FEEr
Type: Package
Title: Functional Extension and Evenness (FEE) index from trait data
Version: 0.5.2
Authors@R: c(
  person(given="Tao", family="Zhang", email="t.zhang05@outlook.com", role=c("aut","cre")),
  person(given="Aditya", family="Gaydhani", role="ctb"),
  person(given="Grant M.", family="Domke", role="ctb"),
  person(given="Matthew B.", family="Russell", role="ctb"),
  person(given="Jeremy W.", family="Lichstein", role="ctb"))
URL: https://github.com/tz05/FEEr
BugReports: https://github.com/tz05/FEEr/issues
Description: A package to calculate the functional extension and evenness 
  (FEE) index. This index measures functional diversity by evaluating the 
  overall extension of species traits and interspecific trait differences 
  of a species assemblage in trait space.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.0.4), foreach, ape, cluster, doSNOW, parallel
Suggests: 
    testthat,
